      <title>德国商业银行因联合信贷银行的做法遭遇反对而倒闭</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-23/commerzbank-stock-drops-as-germany-halts-further-share-sales</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国表示将不再出售德国商业银行股份，导致该银行股价下跌，促使交易员减少了对意大利联合信贷银行 (UniCredit SpA) 收购该银行的押注。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-23/commerzbank-stock-drops-as-germany-halts-further-share-sales</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 23 Sep 2024 07:26:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
